4606-System_Search_AutoSummary:
Sheet1
If epoch is 1970, and the timestamp within the database has the same format as above, use the following formula to convert:
=((((B2/60)/60)/24))+DATE(1970,1,1)

EXAMPLE:
Unix epoch time
Human Readable Timestamp
1524690657.00
4/25/2018 9:10:57 PM
60.00
60.00
24.00
1970.00
1.00
1.00
